Readme
======

       libSFTA : Symbolic Finite Tree Automata library



Installation
============

Follow these steps for successful installation of libSFTA:

  1. Clone the git repository with libSFTA:

    $ git clone git://github.com/ondrik/libsfta.git libsfta

  2. Enter the directory

    $ cd libsfta

  3. Initialize git submodules in the repository

    $ git submodule init

  4. Update git submodules

    $ git submodule update

  5. Generate the Makefile

    $ cd build
    $ cmake ..

  6. Compile the sources

    $ make

  7. Run tests

    $ make test
